    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, that's what's so exhausting. the constant effort to leave \"imprints\" or reach out to people when you feel like you're already a ghost. it feels like a lot of work just to prove you exist. sometimes i just think... why bother fighting to be seen when it would be so much easier to just fade away completely? wouldn't it be more peaceful to just let the silence win?",
